%BA%A5t-t%E1%BB%8Bch-tu%C3%BD-%C4%91%C3%A1p-Qu%C3%A2n-%C4%90%C3%B4ng/poem-9Lr_Xakcdd5HyCBHU407uw">Thất tịch tuý đáp Quân Đông - 七夕醉答君東</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thang-Hi%E1%BB%83n-T%E1%BB%95/author-9UfZr60VQz5UUa1JmQS-sw">Thang Hiển Tổ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-C%E1%BB%91/Thu-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-2kSM12IVW1nrsOTB5vef_w">Thu cảm - 秋感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-C%E1%BB%91/author-BZC85-RUde1Ny-Bhs-zr-A">Vũ Cố</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Tr%C3%A0-L%C4%83ng-tr%C3%BAc-chi-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-05/poem-AqGULPmJseXIK94wjPjB9A">Trà Lăng trúc chi ca kỳ 05 - 茶陵竹枝歌其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-NBWGPHKrPwyFe9z3UQCqkQ">Lý Đông Dương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%A0nh-T%C3%B4n-Du%E1%BA%ADt/X%C3%BA-n%C3%B4-nhi-l%E1%BB%87nh-V%C5%A9-song-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-H%E1%BB%91i-Am-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu-t%C3%AC-b%C3%A0-nh%E1%BA%A1c-ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-aDLdPdqsWMyuyxfOor8nZQ">Xú nô nhi lệnh - Vũ song độc Hối Am điếu tì bà nhạc phủ - 醜奴兒令－雨窗讀悔庵弔琵琶樂府</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%A0nh-T%C3%B4n-Du%E1%BA%ADt/author-nP1V-tl_i1mwn2BJ9gSE-g">Bành Tôn Duật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/Xu%C3%A2n-hi%E1%BB%83u/poem-GpkeuArfeTxtEKHNDANYzQ">Xuân hiểu - 春曉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-EY7jN0xHQfiiJpD91KwIgw">Trần Nhân Tông</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
